Text: This is exactly what I've been waiting for! Thank you so much!

your sharing is nice, to be sure, but if you go to great music website, amg (allmusic.com), and read the reviews for the albums here, only about 1 or 2 of them are truly worth having, this is how I feel about jazz, the birth of a band and the lost man being the biggest ones to find, walking in space and smackwater jack being the best of the bunch. thanks though, it's a great introduction to this prolific man's work. and walking is space is just amazing.
